Attention Newark CSD!

-IT Department Update-

We have made a few changes to our Technology in-person appointments and IT live chat hours. In-person appointments are Monday-Friday, 12-2 instead of just Wednesday and Thursday. The live IT chat hours have changed to 10 - 11 and 3 - 4.

Attached is our IT-help flyer, but the interactive version you can find over on our website at:

https://www.newarkcsd.org/domain/55

Good Afternoon Newark CSD!

Due to the recent events of COVID-19 and the closing of school districts across the country, there has been a rising number of headlines and news articles that paint some darker times for the up-coming months.

Because of this, we will be posting more POSITIVE articles and news from the district on a regular basis. This includes our engagement with you and our great Newark community, and how we will all be adapting to stay positive and healthy during these times.

With that being said, please check out this article on how our Kelley school musicians postponed their RPO concert field trip, but still made the best of it and ended on a high note.

Thank you and enjoy

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Link to article:

https://t.co/TV087sqyDK?amp=1

Written by: Brenda Pittman

Photos by: Dominic Vassallo
